@startuml
title 售后退款流程（含审核 + 补偿）

actor "买家" as buyer
actor "客服" as cs
participant "aftersale-service" as aftersale
participant "workflow-service" as wf
participant "order-core" as order
participant "payment-service" as payment
participant "inventory-service" as inv
queue "RocketMQ" as mq
participant "财务系统" as finance
actor "payment_gw" as payment_gw
participant "notify" as notify
participant "coupon-service" as coupon

== 退款申请 ==
buyer -> aftersale: 申请退款 (订单ID + 原因)
activate aftersale
aftersale -> aftersale: 校验售后时效
aftersale -> aftersale: 校验订单状态（是否可退）
aftersale -> aftersale: 校验退款金额上限

alt 自动审核通过（满足系统规则）
    aftersale -> wf: 启动退款 Saga
    activate wf

    wf -> order: Step 1: 状态更新 PAID → REFUNDING
    activate order
    order -> order: 状态机迁移
    order --> wf: 成功
    deactivate order

    wf -> inv: Step 2: 释放库存
    activate inv
    inv -> inv: 回滚库存预占/扣减
    inv --> wf: 成功
    deactivate inv

    wf -> coupon: Step 3: 释放优惠券
    activate coupon
    coupon -> coupon: 回滚优惠券占用
    coupon --> wf: 成功
    deactivate coupon

    wf -> payment: Step 4: 发起退款（原路返回）
    activate payment
    payment -> payment_gw: 退款请求 (支付宝/微信)
    payment_gw -> payment: 退款成功回调
    payment --> wf: 成功
    deactivate payment

    wf -> order: Step 5: 状态更新 REFUNDING → REFUNDED
    activate order
    order -> order: 状态机迁移
    order --> wf: 成功
    deactivate order

    wf -> finance: Step 6: 推送退款结算数据
    finance --> wf: 成功

    order -> mq: 发布 OrderRefundedEvent
    mq -> notify: 发送退款成功通知

    wf --> aftersale: 退款完成
    aftersale --> buyer: 退款成功

    deactivate wf

else 需要人工审核
    aftersale -> cs: 生成退款审核任务
    note right: 客服工作台待处理

    cs -> aftersale: 审核通过 / 拒绝
    alt 审核通过
        aftersale -> wf: 启动退款 Saga（同自动审核流程）
    else 审核拒绝
        aftersale --> buyer: 拒绝退款 + 原因
    end
end
deactivate aftersale

@enduml
